sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant CTX as AnalysisContext
    participant SM as StorageManager.__init__
    participant R as filesystems.registry.register_all
    participant FAT as fat adapter
    participant TSK as tsk adapter
    participant APFS as apfs adapter

    CTX->>SM: context.storage (lazy property)
    SM->>R: register_all(self)

    Note over R: iterate every adapter module;<br/>each try-imports its optional dep

    R->>FAT: try import
    FAT-->>R: stdlib only, OK
    R->>SM: register_filesystem("fat", FATFilesystem)

    R->>TSK: try import pytsk3
    TSK-->>R: ImportError (optional extra missing)
    Note over R: log.debug("tsk adapter skipped")

    R->>APFS: try import apfs_reader
    APFS-->>R: ImportError
    Note over R: log.debug("apfs adapter skipped")

    R-->>SM: done
    SM-->>CTX: StorageManager ready<br/>filesystems() -> ["fat"]
